<p><strong>Scott:</strong> Oh yeah, for sure. Youre always picking how wide should it be, how deep should it be, how many input this do I need, how many that? What should my learning rate be? And all these different hyper parameters and then you try to use it on some wild data and things arent working. Why arent they working?</p>
